service.name: Supporting Leave for Living Organ Donor
service.description: The Supporting Leave for Living Organ Donor initiative supports paid leave for living organ donors by providing a payment of up to six weeks.  The payment is available to employers whose employees have had time off work either to donate an organ (being either a kidney or partial liver) or to attend medical appointments to assess their suitability to become a living organ donor.
